+ Forcing the program to abort via `die()`.
+ [Editing the php-fpm pool config to catch workers output](https://stackoverflow.com/a/10546138/1354930). Still seems to not do anything.
+ Some suggest I might not be restarting PHP-FPM correctly. I use this command `sudo service php7.0-fpm restart &amp; sudo service nginx restart` based off [this answer](https://stackoverflow.com/a/10546138/1354930).
